    "body": "@prestonvanloon , that sounds like a good idea. \r\n\r\nSo the requirements would be a `config.go` file in the `shared` directory. \r\n\r\nThe `SetEnv` method should accept a second parameter for `beaconchain` or `validator`. If the second parameter is `validator`, `GetConfig` returns a subset of the config with the fields `CollationSizeLimit`, `SlotDuration`, `CycleLength`. \r\n\r\n@cyberbono3 , sorry for the late response and thanks for offering! This issue doesn't delve too deep into the details of shasper, so I hope that what's here provides enough context. Feel free to ask any question in this thread or on our Discord though :+1:",
